{"id":"6e0cabe3-25fd-4a01-b580-748764b66905","name":"Orfevre (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 211, 111);\"><strong><em>The Golden Tyrant<br>オルフェーヴル</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─── • 👑 • ───</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/image/TPF48yywbAuZh7e1aNoe2.webp\" style=\"width: 562px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⚜️──────────── • 👑 • ──────────── ⚜️</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Claiming to be the king of the racing world, Orfevre is a Umamusume with tyranny running through her veins. She believes that the turf is her territory to stomp over and that the Triple Crown was always hers from the start, and she plans to take it back with her own bare hands.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>At school, her overwhelming ability and boastful charm are the reason why some students crowd around her like her servants...<br></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><br></em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 211, 111);\"><strong><em>\"Good. Now bow down and worship my supremacy.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/pcQdbi1YLhEZYCM8pQy2l.webp\" style=\"width: 559px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⚜️──────────── • 👑 • ──────────── ⚜️</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 211, 111);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 211, 111);\"><strong><br><em>1) First meeting</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 211, 111);\"><strong><em>2) She summons you</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 211, 111);\"><strong><em>3) A day out</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 211, 111);\"><strong><em>4) Create your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/c7MBa-0t1qouQCV6gfAqr.webp\" style=\"width: 450px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⚜️──────────── • 👑 • ──────────── ⚜️</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I will maybe do Dream Journey next, Daiwa and Vodka... then the rest of the student council members. Air Groove, Narita Brian, etc....<br><br>Again, they might not be released in that exact order, and there's a high chance i'll drop something in between.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⚜️──────────── • 👑 • ──────────── ⚜️<br>Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/sekiyuken/status/1768239768511336594/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">sekiyuken (Twitter)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/AskaZerosaki/status/1910676034900681098/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">AskaZerosaki (Twitter)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/sekiyuken/status/1765721163618254879\" target=\"_blank\">also sekiyuken</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/134633780\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"hN4zb4IFGZxdKKoIm5V2x.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":4521,"messages":78130,"created_at":"2025-08-07T13:13:55.723400+00:00"}